race.comment: LET IT BEEL (9) looks set to break through. Fourth at Sandown two back then runner-up latest over the mile at Cranbourne when finished off well. This looks ideal and gets chance to get off the mark. MEET THE WIFE (8) has also been running on well, the latest when fourth at the mile at Seymour. Can improve again and looks a strong winning chance. ZA ZA BEST (13) showed ability on debut then had the blinkers added last time but went too keenly and weakened late. Has them removed this time and fitter again can improve sharply. VLTAVA (12) is having just third career start and hasn't been far away with a pair of fifths so far. Blinkers added and worth keeping safe.
race.rail_position: +4m from the 400m to the winning post, True Remainder. (Pent: 5.60)
